Exascale target size (example)

Case 1:
#define _NTX  160
#define _NTY  160
#define _NTZ  160
#define _NTT  160

#define _NDIMX  20
#define _NDIMY  20
#define _NDIMZ  20

Case 2:
#define _NTX  256
#define _NTY  256
#define _NTZ  256
#define _NTT  256

#define _NDIMX  32
#define _NDIMY  32
#define _NDIMZ  32

These examples fix the local spatial volume to 8^3.
